  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> July 22, 2025</p>

  <p>At <strong>LiftorZing</strong>, your privacy is important to us. This policy outlines how we handle your data.</p>

  <h2>1. No Personal Data Collected</h2>
  <p>You can use LiftorZing without registering, logging in, or providing any contact details. We do not collect any personal information directly.</p>

  <h2>2. Uploaded Images</h2>
  <p>When you upload a photo, it is temporarily processed by our backend to generate a fun response. We do not store, save, or share any images you upload.</p>

  <h2>3. Third-Party AI Services</h2>
  <p>We use services like Hugging Face to generate responses. Your input (text or image) may be processed by their servers, but we do not control how they handle this data. Review their privacy policies for more information.</p>

  <h2>4. Cookies and Tracking</h2>
  <p>We use cookies through Google Analytics to help us understand how visitors use LiftorZing and to improve user experience.</p>
  <p>You can opt out of Google Analytics tracking using browser extensions or by disabling cookies in your browser settings.</p>

  <h2>5. Children's Privacy</h2>
  <p>LiftorZing is designed for users age 13 and up. We do not knowingly collect data from children under 13.</p>

  <h2>6. Changes to this Policy</h2>
  <p>We may update this policy occasionally. Any major changes will be noted on this page.</p>

  <h2>7. Contact</h2>
  <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:pickaside@liftorzing.com">pickaside@liftorzing.com</a></p>
